---
// Problem/Solution Section - focus on personalized AI + agents
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16">
      <!-- Problem -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-faded)]">
          The Problem
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-3xl">
          AI isn't really personalized to you
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Every AI tool treats you like a stranger. It doesn't know your projects, 
          your preferences, or how you work. You're constantly re-explaining context, 
          spawning generic agents that don't fit your needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Solution -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-faded)]">
          The Solution
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-3xl">
          An AI system built around you
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          OpenAgent is a configuration layer for OpenCode that makes AI truly personal.
          Persistent memory, specialized agents tailored to your workflow, 
          and a system that evolves with your needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
